Metrics defined at level record for token classification must be normalized following next data structure: 

```python
{
  #...common record metrics
  "predicted": {
    #...metrics related to predicted data
  },
  "annotated": {
    #...metrics related to annotated data
  }
}
```

For token classification:

```python
{
  "tokens_length": ...,
  "annotated": {
    "mentions": {
      "value": ...,
      "label": ...,
      ...
    }
  },
  "predicted": {
    "mentions": {
      "value": ...,
      "label": ...,
      ...
    }
  }
}
```

